	(text " Area                | Note                                                                                                 \n ------------------- | -------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------\n Input cap placement | C1/C2 on VIN_SOLAR are BQ24074 input capacitors. Place close to U2 IN/VSS                             \n OUT rail meaning    | SYS_RAW is NOT 3.3V. It is BQ24074 power-path output. Feed SYS_RAW into the 3.3V buck-boost regulator\n BAT rail meaning    | BAT_RAW is raw 1S Li-ion/LiPo battery node. Nominal ~3.7V, full 4.2V                                 \n Charge current      | R2 sets fast-charge current. 8.87k/8.9k ≈ 100mA target                                               \n Input current mode  | EN1=GND and EN2=GND selects USB100 mode, ~100mA input current limit                                  \n ILIM                | R1 keeps ILIM valid. Use 8.0k max. Only active if EN2=HIGH and EN1=LOW                               \n TS                  | TS fixed with 10k to GND because battery is 2-wire. No real battery temperature protection           \n Status pins         | CHARGER_CHG_N and CHARGER_PGOOD_N are active-low open-drain outputs. Pull up to 3V3_SYS only. No LEDs\n TMR                 | JP_TMR_DISABLE open: safety timer set by R7=72k. JP closed: TMR tied to GND, safety timer disabled\n Power pad           | EP must connect to GND plane with vias. VSS pin still needs normal GND connection\n Caps near pins      | C3 close to BAT/VSS. C4 close to OUT/VSS\n"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 273.05 135.636 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(face "Adwaita Mono")
				(size 0.762 0.762)
			)
			(justify left top)
		)
		(uuid "f54dab82-5985-4f5f-9a05-4e722ffc489c")
	)
